entries.femaleVariant: Yeah?!
Aaron? It's V. I've got the scrolls.
So? Hit any snags 'long the way?
[Give recordings] Here you go.
They're for the investigation, right?
I've seen what's on them.
Here – take 'em.
Great work. I'll spread the word you do solid mercwork. Comin' from Aaron McCarlson, that'll go far.
These scrolls are for some kinda investigation, right?
Mhm. Real big stink, mind you. But thanks to your help I can give it a push.
Kinda sad to let 'em go. Contents are truly fascinating.
You weren't supposed to watch 'em. That was the deal.
Surprise – it's money.
I want you behind bars.
What do you think, Aaron? A ticket to Corporate Wars? A foot massage?
All right, for fuck's sake, I get it. I'll pay you double.
Don't want anything from you.
So then what the fuck's your deal?
What I want's for you to be behind bars, where you belong.
Too bad. Not gonna happen.
Don't want anything.
The fucking dirtbag...
Oh, V, ahem. Thought you were another one of those Serenity Bible whackjobs. Come in.
You're real tough as nails, huh? That's how you survive out there.
There always are. Handled 'em.
I'm sure it will. Take care.
Oh, now you wanna go by the book, huh? Scrolls didn't paint such a law-abidin' picture o' you.
Save the moralizing bullshit. Guessin' you want somethin', so just spill already.
I just like watching shitbags like you break into a sweat – the moment when you're not as untouchable as you thought you were.
How fuckin' professional of ya.
And thus the pot calls the kettle black.
Your scrolls – take 'em. And don't make me wait for those eddies.
These things still surprise you?
Fifty years in soul prison gives you a break from this, even if it was only a blip.
Lucky you.
Hey, V... make sure he fucking regrets this. Pretty please?
Are you trying to see how fucking low you can sink in Night City?
Let's get one thing straight, Johnny. You're not my conscience.
Yeah, good. What a shitty gig that'd be.
Looks like my dream came true.
You know me. I'm a people-pleaser.
All right, now hand over those scrolls already. Choppity chop chop.
Nope. Might as well've been a ghost.
You do a quiet job, huh? Don't show off – I admire that.
